<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>Āsīdvinītō dvijapārijātō nidhirgguṇānāṁ bhuvi celviseṭṭiḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> tatassutōbhūdeṟaga<unclear>ssu</unclear>śīlaḥ priyā
<lb n="2"/>tadīyābhavadeṟṟakāṁbā <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> tābhyāṁ sutābhūtkalakaṁṭhakaṁṭhī sūrāṁbikā biṁbaphalā<unclear>dharōṣṭhi</unclear> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> tasyāssuke
<lb n="3" break="no"/>śyāstanayēha jātā prōlāṁbikā pūrṇnaśaśāṁkkavaktrā <supplied reason="omitted">2</supplied> śakādhipābdē dahanādrikhēṁddu<unclear>mitē</unclear> tithau kārttika
<lb n="4" break="no"/>pūrṇnimāyāṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> prōlāṁbikā dīpamadādiyaṁ sā śrībhīmanāthāya sukēśyakhaṇḍaṁ [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 3*] <unclear>yidi</unclear> prōlama diviya
<lb n="5"/><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> Āsīdvinītō dvijapārijātō nidhirgguṇānāṁ bhuvi celviseṭṭiḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> tatassutōbhūdeṟagassuśīla<unclear>ḥ pri</unclear>yā tadīyābha
<lb n="6" break="no"/>vadeṟṟakāṁbā [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 4*] tā(ṁ)bhyāṁ sutā bhūdibhakuṁbhatuṁgaghanastanadvaṁdvabharānatāṁgī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> sūrāṁbi<unclear>kā</unclear> biṁbaphalādharō
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṣṭi lōkērtthināṁ jaṁgamakalpavallī [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 5*] śakādhipābdē dahanādrikhēṁddumitē tithau kārttikapūrṇnimāyāṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> sūrāṁbikā<note n="378-1">The few more lines after this are too faintly engraved to be deciphered.</note>
</p>

